## Resulting Dependency Graph

```
types                (no internal imports)
gamestatus           → types
cards                → types
board                → cards, types
gameactions          → domain, board, cards, gamestatus, types
domain               → board, cards, gamestatus, types
websocket            → domain, gameactions, cards, gamestatus, types
```

No cycles. `ports` is gone.

